    Black Aracnia walked up to Quicky, "Dont worry. Im here. And Hell Beast 
wont do anything. Hes to much of a coward. But where is Tarantulas....and 
Aerostreak for that matter?"

    Tarantulas, and Aerostreak, found the fallen pod close to the base. It 
was a beautiful site, and the treasure inside was priceless. Now they had to 
get it programmed.
    "Aerostreak, I think Ive done it! Step back, the form I have chosen is 
quite....interesting." He said and stepped back as the lid poped open.
    The halwk looked at him. "What is it?" And then looked to the pod. (This 
is where the owner of the bot steps in...hint hint....)

    Megatron saw the pod, and slammed is fist down. "Damn it! There after 
that pod! Argh!!!!!! I want that pod!"
